  "description": "Tiny Swords and Tools for PVP (includes PVP Crosshair too!)",
  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/684/717/cbf4e971-7207-4602-bd76-b44081f9b7df.png\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/420/241/tiny-pvp-swords-and-tool.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"952\" height=\"62\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Resource Pack-16x-green?style=plastic\" /> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/gamerpotion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/buy me a coffee-support-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/uCPfPBvsRJ\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/870825743788158986?color=blue&amp;style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/GamerPotionDev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/my other-projects-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/get%20a%20server-click%20here-blue?style=plastic\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>I made this pack to use with my <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/best-pvp\">Best PVP modpack</a> and thought of releasing as a standalone. All swords have been cut down in photoshop by 5x5 px and reduced in size. Tools have been reduced by 4x4 px.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This will further improve your vanilla experience by having smaller weps and tools giving more screen area and is very useful for PVP. All the textures are from the vanilla game but in a smaller size.</p>\n<p>This pack also includes a PVP Crosshair.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/420/240/untitled-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/457/563/2022-04-26_22.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/434/158/dec51e74-03ba-4abb-920c-bdc47a4e302a.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ko-fi.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/brandasset/kofi_bg_tag_dark.png\" width=\"341\" height=\"129\" /></a></p>",
